    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/409f40987fa79bc6fbadd57ebe7f59a9.poster.avif?t=1771798325\" width=878 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/409f40987fa79bc6fbadd57ebe7f59a9.webm?t=1771798325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight in the shifting darkness</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through a living, mysterious labyrinth where danger lurks in every corner. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in combat which blends fast-paced <strong>hack’n’slash</strong> action with the weight and precision of <strong>souls-like</strong> games. All this served in classic <strong>roguelike</strong> fashion.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/29030dbd9580eb91a266045224f9ee8c.webp?t=1771798325\" width=614 height=1 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/b29f63c97a8e379b6804c8e5a027c59a.poster.avif?t=1771798325\" width=878 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/b29f63c97a8e379b6804c8e5a027c59a.webm?t=1771798325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft your power</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find gear, enchant weapons and make your artifacts more powerful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into deep itemization systems - <strong>Caveshifter</strong> is designed around build variety, character customization and meaningful progression. Your inventory is limited to a weapon and two powerful trinkets, so... choose wisely and take good care of them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/29030dbd9580eb91a266045224f9ee8c.webp?t=1771798325\" width=614 height=1 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/2510738ec3d5342a7a71526bf5e1a0af.poster.avif?t=1771798325\" width=878 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/2510738ec3d5342a7a71526bf5e1a0af.webm?t=1771798325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft your... dungeons?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use powerful runes to shift the path ahead. Choose your rewards, alter enemies, or summon new rooms. Embrace the Caves - decide if they oppose you or serve you.</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/29030dbd9580eb91a266045224f9ee8c.webp?t=1771798325\" width=614 height=1 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/60382c019d284a7912337d87d415dab4.poster.avif?t=1771798325\" width=878 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132310/extras/60382c019d284a7912337d87d415dab4.webm?t=1771798325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the unknown</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run is different - new rooms, new choices, new rewards. Explore a large ever-changing network of caves and uncover all of its secrets. This game is built around <strong>replayability</strong> as a core design pillar. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
